# EMCAP — Documentation sync (mandatory)

**Every implementation PR or task completion MUST update docs in the same change.**  
Code without doc updates is **not Done**.

Recipe: `docs/dev/recipes/sync-docs-after-change.md`

## Minimum checklist (always)

| # | Document | When |
|---|----------|------|
| 1 | `plan/03-task-backlog.md` | Task status changed |
| 2 | Relevant matrix row | See matrix map below |
| 3 | `docs/dev/codebase-index.md` | New paths, zones, tests, scripts |
| 4 | `docs/dev/known-pitfalls.md` | New regression or fix worth remembering |
| 5 | Matching recipe in `docs/dev/recipes/` | Steps or paths changed |
| 6 | `.cursor/skills/` if agent guidance changed | New patterns, wrong paths removed |

## Matrix map (use the right one)

| Change type | Update |
|-------------|--------|
| Platform API / service wired | `spec/sdd/04-capability-matrix.md` |
| CRUD / renderer / entity UX | `spec/sdd/05-end-user-matrix.md` |
| Shell, admin UI, settings, themes, i18n | `spec/sdd/06-admin-product-ui-matrix.md` |
| New FR / requirement coverage | `spec/sdd/03-traceability-matrix.md` + `01-requirements.md` if new ID |
| Phase playbook scope | `plan/12-enterprise-product-ui.md` or phase playbook |
| Major milestone | `spec/sdd/00-document-control.md` revision row |

**Never** mark UX/admin Done using only matrix 04 or 05.

## Web UI changes — also update

- `clients/web/src/app/shared/README.md` — new or changed reusable component
- `plan/12-phase12-dod-checklist.md` — if DoD gates change
- `README.md` — if entry points or key docs change

## Phase 12 UI — also update

- `spec/sdd/06-admin-product-ui-matrix.md` (required)
- Skill `emcap-enterprise-ui` — paths and shared component list
- `docs/dev/recipes/enterprise-ui-shell.md` or `add-admin-api-and-ui.md`

## Anti-patterns (block merge / Done)

- Task marked Done; backlog still Pending
- New component under `shared/`; `codebase-index.md` unchanged
- Recipe still references deleted paths (e.g. flat `shell.component` nav)
- Skills say "TBD" or stale task counts
